dcterms:description: The Leaf River data set consists of 40 years (WY 1949-1988) of daily data from the Leaf River Basin in southern Mississippi, USA, including cumulative daily values of observed mean areal precipitation, potential evapotranspiration, and watershed outlet streamflow.
